&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ffxivrotations.com/3et8"&gt;Level 50 Opener&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rotate through your combos and smash that Midare button. Use Meikyo for Gekko and Kasha past the opener. Refresh Higanbana as close to 0 as possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="level-52"&gt;Level 52&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Introduces Kenki Gauge and Hissatsu: Shinten. Use it when you want and be sure not to overcap.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="level-60"&gt;Level 60&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ffxivrotations.com/3lvo"&gt;Level 60 Opener&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once you begin accruing Kenki to spend on Shinten, the opener should look like this.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Basic Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/basic-guide/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 02:52:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/basic-guide/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="foreword"&gt;Foreword&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-Zheng&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As of Dawntrail, Samurai has been part of the game for seven years. As part of the team, I am updating this guide for Dawntrail as we have gotten a substantial amount of changes upon release, until 7.05 which marked a big shift in gameplay since Shadowbringers, and will be covered in this document. This guide is intended for newer and older players alike.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The following section summarizes Samurai’s abilities. You may also refer to &lt;a href="https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/jobguide/samurai/"&gt;Square Enix’s Samurai Job Guide&lt;/a&gt; for specific skill and trait text. Feel free to skip this section if you are familiar with Samurai’s skills.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Skills Overview</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/skills-overview/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 02:48:24 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/skills-overview/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="global-cooldown-actions-single-target"&gt;Global Cooldown Actions (Single Target)&lt;/h1&gt;
