 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;
&lt;div class="md__image"&gt;
 &lt;img src="https://xivapi.com/i/003000/003166_hr1.png" onclick="openModal(this)" alt="Yukikaze" /&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Yukikaze&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Single target second step combo. 160 potency, 340 potency if combo from Hakaze. Combo Bonus: Setsu Sen, +15 Kenki.&lt;/td&gt;
