&lt;br&gt;
*To one of the recommended SkS ranges.\&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Viable GCD/SkS ranges (with Shifu counted):\&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
